casebody.data:
Nathan B. Kogan, as Executor of Mary Winter, Deceased, Respondent, v. Gustave Bondy, Defendant. Charles Bondy, as Executor of Gustave Bondy, Deceased, Appellant.

Reported below, 264 App. Div. 717.

Submitted July 29, 1942; decided October 15, 1942. Nathan B. Kogan and Joseph S. Robinson for motion. Leonard Acker opposed.

Motion dismissed, with ten dollars costs and necessary printing disbursements. The order is one of reversal and does not finally determine the action.
